snippet.title: Super Motherload PS4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Motherload is now available for PlayStation®4 and PlayStation®3!

Enter the Super Motherload Puzzle Contest!
http://forums.xgenstudios.com/showthread.php?255467-Super-Motherload-Puzzles-and-Features-Contest!

For more info, check out www.supermotherload.com

Super Motherload is a digging adventure with a procedurally-generated world that changes each time you play. Purchase powerful upgrades and supplies for your mining pod as you progress and prosper.
